I consulted the Doctor on 15 Aug 2021 for my son who had a boil. He examined him very well, addressed our concerns, and prescribed required medication which helped in speedy recovery. Despite having a packed schedule, the Doctor is punctual, handles children and parents in a very gentle manner for best possible medicare. Kudos to you Doctor, your staff and the online Practo Team for the brave and relentless efforts delivered through this extra-ordinary pandemic period of 1.5 years in bringing the best medicare to the comfort of peoples' homes. God bless. Best Wishes for a very Happy and Healthy Vijayadasami. 🙏 Best Regards, Navaraj Tamang

I am a regular visitor to his clinic for my one year old daughter. We have visited various paeditrician in Delhi NCR in last one year but no doubt to say he is one of the best paeditrician of Delhi. Since birth my daughter has faced many health problems. Dr. Kalyan handled her case every time very deligently. He listens carefully to parents and take a note of all minutest details of the case and than suggest very practical solution. There are times when we were very disturbed because of my daughter health but by following his treatment, she managed to improve everytime. I never found him prescribing unnessesary medicine. These days I am also visiting him regular vaccination of my daughter. Would like to express my gratitude to Dr. Kalyan for being patient and caring for my daughter.

Dr. Das was very patient dealing with my son. He explained everything in great details which was really helpful for me. I would definitely like to say my experience was wonderful and would definitely recommend other parents to him as he is great in his job. Thank you sir 🙏

Doctor was fantastic and he heard me very patiently, reviewed all my previous medicine, discussed each of my reports which I shared and then discussed the prescription and what line of treatment he is following, making me understand all the affect of medication. I am really impressed and he gave me sufficient time. Thanks so much to Dr. Kalyanashish Das.
